#sike site

##How to run this app

- create config.yml (using config_sample.yml as example)
- rake db:setup
- bower install
- rails server

# Start Up

```
foreman start
```

# Environment Variables

+ RAILS_ROOT: the root directory of the app
+ RAILS_ENV: the environment of the app
+ PUMA_CONTROL_TOKEN: a string token used to access the puma control
  + If presents, the control starts on port 9293.
  + curl :9293/restart?token=foobar
  + to restart, `pumactl  -C tcp://localhost:9293 -T foobar restart`